							<span class="inline-block py-px px-2 mb-4 text-xs leading-5 text-yellow-500 bg-yellow-100 font-medium uppercase rounded-9xl">
								Kontakt
							</span>
							<h3 class="mb-4 text-4xl md:text-5xl text-darkCoolGray-900 font-bold tracking-tighter leading-tight">
								Meld dich doch mal ...
